  "title": "Site Manager (LTA Projects/Infrastructure, East Region)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Coordinate equipment and manpower for site operations.</li><li>Supervise and manage assigned site works.</li><li>Plan and control operations to ensure efficiency and productivity.</li><li>Minimize material wastage and ensure timely project completion.</li><li>Liaise with clients on site matters and follow up on required actions.</li><li>Ensure routine machine maintenance and good site housekeeping.</li><li>Report work progress, issues, and cost-saving opportunities.</li><li>Perform other duties as assigned by management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 8 years of local construction site experience, preferably with LTA project experience.</li></ul><p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p><p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p><p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p><p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p><p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
